#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1129
#: input:1129 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Accommodation for your people. Also stores your wares and tools."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1131
#: input:1131 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The headquarters is your main building."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Headquarters
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1133
#: input:1133 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We founded this new colony, now go with Lutas and do the best you can do for "
"your tribe."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Headquarters
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1135
#: input:1135 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Priestess of Lutas inaugurating you as leader of the Atleantean tribe"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean warehouse: Warehouse
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1142
#: input:1142 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Your workers and soldiers will find shelter here. Also stores your wares and "
"tools. It will help you to stabilize your economy."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Warehouse
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1145
#: input:1145 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Maybe you think it’s a boring task to store, count and retrieve all this "
"stuff, but do you really want your carriers to walk all the way to your "
"Headquarters?"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Headquarters
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1148
#: input:1148 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Head of the warehouse"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean warehouse: Port
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1155
#: input:1155 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean warehouse: Port
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1157
#: input:1157 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Similar to the Headquarters a Port can be attacked and destroyed by an "
"enemy. It is recommendable to send soldiers to defend it."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Port
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1159
#: input:1159 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"This is the building where expeditions will be equipped to boldly go and "
"find new shores."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Port
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1161
#: input:1161 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The designer of the new Expedition ship class, during the opening of a new "
"Port"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Quarry
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1169
#: input:1169 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Cuts blocks of granite out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Quarry
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1171
#: input:1171 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The quarry needs rocks to cut within the work area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Quarry
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1173
#: input:1173 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"You must not assume Atlanteans will play everything soft, there are hard "
"times we cannot avoid."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Quarry
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1175
#: input:1175 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Priestess of Lutas asked why stones are needed for buildings"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Quarry, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1178
#: input:1178 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one granite between %1$s and %2$s, depending on "
"how far the stonecutter has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Woodcutter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1188
#: input:1188 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Fells trees in the surrounding area and processes them into logs."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Woodcutter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1190
#: input:1190 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The woodcutter’s house needs trees to fell within the work area. The "
"woodcutter in this house is %1$s faster than a normal Atlantean woodcutter."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Woodcutter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1192
#: input:1192 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We want to fell trees in a clean and dignified way, therefore we use saws. "
"An ax is a tool used by other tribes only."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Woodcutter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1194
#: input:1194 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Atlantean woodcutter asked why saws are used to cut trees"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Woodcutter's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1197
#: input:1197 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one log between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the woodcutter has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Forester's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1207
#: input:1207 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Plants trees in the surrounding area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Forester's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1209
#: input:1209 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The forester’s house needs free space within the work area to plant the "
"trees."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Forester's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1211
#: input:1211 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"‘Only after the last tree has been cut<br>Only after the last forest was "
"devastated<br>Only after the last piece of green has become bare "
"soil<br>Then will you find that nature needs to be cared for.’"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Forester's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1216
#: input:1216 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Prophecy of the foresters’ guild"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Forester's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1219
#: input:1219 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The forester plants one tree between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how far he "
"has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1229
#: input:1229 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Fishes on the coast near the fisher’s house and collects seashells too."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1232
#: input:1232 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The fisher’s house needs water full of fish within the work area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1234
#: input:1234 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Build a fish breeder’s house close to the fisher’s house to make sure that "
"you don’t run out of fish."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House, part 3
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1236
#: input:1236 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Roads and trees along the shoreline block fishing."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House use some local fise song as you like
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1239
#: input:1239 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"‘Take your net and come to the sea<br>In the early morning the moon ya still "
"see<br>Collect ya catch by net or by spear,<br>and don’t forget to give "
"Lutas his share.’"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note lore_autor for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fisher's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1244
#: input:1244 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A song from the fishers’ guild"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Atlantean production site: Fisher's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1247
#: input:1247 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The fisher can catch two fishes and collect one seashell between %1$s and "
"%2$s, depending on how far he has to walk. If there are no seashells, it "
"takes between %3$s and %4$s to catch one fish."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fish Breeder's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1257
#: input:1257 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Breeds fish."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fish Breeder's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1259
#: input:1259 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The fish breeder needs open access to the coast."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fish Breeder's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1261
#: input:1261 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"‘Only after the last duck has been shot down<br>Only after the last deer has "
"been put to death<br>Only after the last fish has been caught<br>Then will "
"you find that spiders are not to be eaten.’"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Fish Breeder's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1266
#: input:1266 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Prophecy of the fish breeders"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Hunter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1273
#: input:1273 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Hunts animals to produce meat."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Hunter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1275
#: input:1275 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The hunter’s house needs animals to hunt within the work area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Hunter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1277
#: input:1277 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Sometimes we end up in a region with no fish, so we must hunt. Game will "
"reproduce by itself, if not hunted too much. But yes, fish is our main meal."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Hunter's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1280
#: input:1280 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Hunter answering a fisher"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Hunter's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1283
#: input:1283 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one meat between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the hunter has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1293
#: input:1293 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Draws water out of the deep."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1295
#: input:1295 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "I hope you have checked this spot with a geologist."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1297
#: input:1297 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Well, there is no wellbeing without a well."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1299
#: input:1299 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Water carrier muttering to himself"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1302
#: input:1302 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The carrier needs %s to get one bucket full of water."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Well, part 2
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1304
#: input:1304 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "If the water resource is depleted, the carrier needs %s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Spinning Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1312
#: input:1312 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Spins gold thread out of gold."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Spinning Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1314
#: input:1314 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Do not build until you have a steady gold supply."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Spinning Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1316
#: input:1316 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"No, we can’t spin gold thread from straw. We need real gold. What kind of "
"fairy tale did you get that idea from?"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Gold Spinning Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1318
#: input:1318 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Painted on a gold spinning mill without supplies"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Special helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Scout's House without road connection
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1325
#: input:1325 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"You need to connect this flag to a scout’s house before you can send a scout "
"here."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Scout's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1327
#: input:1327 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Explores unknown territory."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Scout's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1329
#: input:1329 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Will need fish and bread to have his meal the Atlantean way."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Scout's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1331
#: input:1331 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"You do not see everything from your high towers. Sometimes you need someone "
"to find out in person, that’s me!"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Scout's House
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1333
#: input:1333 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A scout answering a soldier"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Scout's House, part 1
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1336
#: input:1336 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "One exploration trip of the scout takes between %1$s and %2$s."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Sawmill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1348
#: input:1348 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Saws logs to produce planks."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Sawmill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1350
#: input:1350 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Will need at least four woodcutters for a constant supply of planks."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Sawmill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1352
#: input:1352 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"The design of our sawmills makes operation simple, yet powerful. Patent "
"pending."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Sawmill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1354
#: input:1354 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Askadus, Inventor of the vertical axis windmill"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Sawmill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1356
#: input:1356 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The sawmill needs %s on average to produce one plank."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smokery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1363
#: input:1363 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Smokes meat and fish to feed the scouts and miners and to train soldiers in "
"the dungeon, labyrinth and temple."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Smokery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1365
#: input:1365 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We are using pure logs, no other ingredients! Which drunken foreigner hath "
"told you that myth?"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Smokery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1367
#: input:1367 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A Smoker answering a passer-by"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smokery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1369
#: input:1369 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all kinds of smoked food are needed "
"by the economy, production of one smoked fish takes %1$s and one smoked meat "
"takes %2$s on average. If only one kind of food is needed by the economy, "
"production of one smoked fish takes %3$s and one smoked meat takes %4$s on "
"average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1377
#: input:1377 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Grinds blackroots and corn to produce blackroot flour and cornmeal, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1379
#: input:1379 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"When no cornmeal is required, the mill will try to produce blackroot flour "
"even when there is no demand for it."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1381
#: input:1381 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We invented this vertical axis design first, the sawmill just copied our "
"ideas but never acknowledged our claim."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1383
#: input:1383 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Miller arguing with a sawyer"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Mill
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1385
#: input:1385 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and both kinds of flour are needed by the "
"economy, production of one sack of each kind of flour takes %1$s on average. "
"If only one kind of flour is needed by the economy, its production takes "
"%2$s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Bakery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1392
#: input:1392 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Bakes bread to feed the scouts and miners and to train soldiers."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Bakery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1394
#: input:1394 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Will need cornmeal and blackroot flour."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Bakery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1396
#: input:1396 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"You cannot compare our bread to anything from those other tribes. This "
"recipe was inherited for generations. It is more nutritious than that paper-"
"like bread you find elsewhere. And it is needed for the personal rite of "
"preparing one’s meal. May God bless you."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Bakery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1400
#: input:1400 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Head of the bakers’ guild"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Bakery
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1402
#: input:1402 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, this building can produce one "
"bread in %s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1409
#: input:1409 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Burns logs into charcoal."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1411
#: input:1411 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Build only if you absolutely must produce some coal, or when you have a very "
"large amount of logs."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1413
#: input:1413 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We must admit that this business is not really the Atlantean way, but in "
"times of need we do what’s necessary."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1415
#: input:1415 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A black voice from inside the charcoal kiln"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1417
#: input:1417 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "The charcoal kiln needs %s on average to produce one coal."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smelting Works
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1424
#: input:1424 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Smelts iron ore into iron and gold ore into gold."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smelting Works
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1426
#: input:1426 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"We learned the smelting from our forefathers, a basic craftsmanship taming "
"the fire and the ore into pure metals."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smelting Works
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1428
#: input:1428 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "A member of the smelters’ guild"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Smelting Works
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1430
#: input:1430 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all metals are needed by the economy, "
"production of one iron takes %1$s and one gold takes %2$s on average. If "
"only one kind of metal is needed by the economy, production of one iron "
"takes %3$s and one gold takes %4$s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Toolsmithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1437
#: input:1437 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Forges all the tools that your workers need."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Toolsmithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1439
#: input:1439 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "People’s power working for the benefit of all"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Toolsmithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1441
#: input:1441 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid "Faded sign found on top of this building"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Toolsmithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1443
#: input:1443 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all tools are needed by the economy, "
"production of one of each tool takes %1$s on average. If only one kind of "
"tool is needed by the economy, its production takes %2$s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site: Weapon Smithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1450
#: input:1450 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"Forges tridents to equip the soldiers and to train their attack in the "
"dungeon."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Lutas’ Atlantean production site:  Weapon Smithy
#: addons/lutas_atlanteans.wad/tribes/lutas_atlanteans_tribe/units.lua:1452
#: input:1452 standard
msgctxt "lutas_atlanteans_building"
msgid ""
"You hear that sound of metal strident? The weapon smith just forged a "
"trident!"
msgstr ""

